Call me elitist, but the sheer number of stupid people in the world is staggering.  Most of them are irresponsible, too.  It is NOT, however, the role of the government to interfere with these people any more than with more intelligent ones, unless they abuse their freedom by committing criminal actions.  To suggest anything else would be a violation of the freedoms which every man and woman possesses.  If you value your freedom so little, that's fine.  I will fight tooth and nail, however, to salvage MY freedoms from the political bonfire onto which you and people like you perversely continue to throw them in the name of safety.<br>
